          <li>• Basic no-show recovery + review request</li>
          <li>• Monthly KPI snapshot (Kept, Rebooks, Reviews)</li>
        </ul>

        <!-- Support line -->
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm rounded-lg px-3 py-2 ring-1 ring-white/30 bg-white/55">
          <strong>Priority support</strong> via WhatsApp & email — business-hours response.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-6">
          <a class="btn btn-primary w-full md:w-auto" href="/contact/">Book a 10-min demo</a>
        </div>

        <!-- Collapsed details to reduce clutter -->
        <div class="mt-5 space-y-3">
          <details class="rounded-xl ring-1 ring-white/30 bg-white/25 p-4 [&_summary]:list-none">
            <summary class="cursor-pointer font-semibold">Setup (one-time)</summary>
            <ul class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-700/90 list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
              <li>Interakt/WABA guidance & template submission</li>
              <li>Booking link wiring & go-live windows</li>
              <li>Staff saved replies (/handoff, /offer, /confirm)</li>
            </ul>
          </details>
          <details class="rounded-xl ring-1 ring-white/30 bg-white/25 p-4 [&_summary]:list-none">
            <summary class="cursor-pointer font-semibold">Ongoing monthly</summary>
