              <li>Template maintenance & timing tweaks</li>
              <li>KPI check & light optimization</li>
              <li>Deliverability & compliance guardrails</li>
            </ul>
          </details>
          <details class="rounded-xl ring-1 ring-white/30 bg-white/25 p-4 [&_summary]:list-none">
            <summary class="cursor-pointer font-semibold">Limits</summary>
            <ul class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-700/90 list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
              <li>Up to <strong>300 messages / month</strong></li>
              <li>1 location · English only by default</li>
              <li>Email snapshot reporting</li>
              <li><strong>WhatsApp/Meta API & conversation fees billed separately</strong> by your BSP/Meta</li>
            </ul>
          </details>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- CLINIC — MOST POPULAR -->
      <div class="group rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-7 ring-2 ring-blue-400/50 bg-white/40 backdrop-blur shadow-lg relative overflow-hidden">
        <span class="absolute top-3 right-3 text-[11px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full ring-1 ring-black/10 bg-white/80">
          Most popular
        </span>

        <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-600/90">2–10 providers</div>
        <h3 class="mt-1 font-extrabold text-2xl">Clinic</h3>
